snippet.title: FREE DLC Cleared for Transfer | Prison Architect
snippet.description:
Check out Prison Architect: Psych Ward: Warden Edition on Paradox https://www.paradoxplaza.com/prison-a...

Your prison will be more lively than ever with the arrival of the criminally insane. Lucky for you, it’s time to outfit your prison with the latest and greatest in Psych Ward management to house these unpredictable inmates.
